high_descs: Turn to the left, then left again and locate the trash can on the floor.
Pick up the bar of soap from the toilet tank.
Carry the bar of soap and turn around. Move across the room and turn left to locate the sink.
Place the soap in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the soap.
Carry the soap and turn around but face to the left right away, with the yellow spray bottle.
Place the bar of soap on the shelf, to the left of the bottle.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a bar of soap and place it on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the trash can on the right side of the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap off the top of the toilet.
Turn around and head to the front of the sink.
Place the soap in the sink and turn the water on and wash off the bar soap and remove it after you turn the water off.
Turn around to the table underneath the towel.
Place the soap on of the table between the candle and cleaning spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Wash off bar of soap and put on table beneath the towel.

high_descs: Turn left, hang a left at the tub and walk to the gray bin by the wall next to the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap from the right side of the toilet tank.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the bar of soap inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the white dresser on the left.
Put the rinsed bar of soap in between the spray bottle and the candle on the right side of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap on a dresser.
